^-|CP||fp||CP|8|at|^B@2^Z@3T|CP||FP||at|here are other reasons as well, but those three cover the vast majority of the cases of when to delay. Having said that, you still should draw trump as soon as possible, unless there is a good reason not to.|
PG| ***** 8 ***** |


AT|

